title: Sweet Cane Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Hawaiian
description: Relocated from 1472 Kilauea Ave. Offers organic sugarcane juice plus smoothies, sandwiches, wraps, acai bowls. Also sells pre-made items like cookies, kale chips, fruit leather, dried banana. Has a small produce stand and a fridge stocked with products like coconut cane pudding, coconut yogurt, probiotic sauerkraut, and juices.
